00:39:24.050 --> 00:39:25.730 align:middle line:84%
I really look at
my experiences--

00:39:25.730 --> 00:39:28.430 align:middle line:90%
and I'm on an evolving journey.

00:39:28.430 --> 00:39:30.570 align:middle line:90%
I really look at my experiences.

00:39:30.570 --> 00:39:33.200 align:middle line:84%
And I think to
myself, wow, if only

00:39:33.200 --> 00:39:38.390 align:middle line:84%
I knew the lives that my
experiences would touch.

00:39:38.390 --> 00:39:40.130 align:middle line:90%
And it's not me.

00:39:40.130 --> 00:39:44.250 align:middle line:84%
It's not me is this person that
feels like a seven-year-old kid

00:39:44.250 --> 00:39:45.050 align:middle line:90%
inside.

00:39:45.050 --> 00:39:46.925 align:middle line:84%
Because if you said,
let's go roller skating,

00:39:46.925 --> 00:39:48.630 align:middle line:90%
I'd be with you in a heartbeat.

00:39:48.630 --> 00:39:50.300 align:middle line:90%
So it's not actually me.

00:39:50.300 --> 00:39:52.520 align:middle line:90%
It's the experiences.

00:39:52.520 --> 00:39:56.750 align:middle line:84%
And it's what was produced as
a result of those experiences

00:39:56.750 --> 00:40:00.950 align:middle line:84%
that have been my greatest
teachers and show me who I am.

00:40:00.950 --> 00:40:05.420 align:middle line:84%
And what I've also realized
is that we are all the same.

00:40:05.420 --> 00:40:06.760 align:middle line:90%
We are all the same.

00:40:06.760 --> 00:40:08.630 align:middle line:84%
We come wrapped in
different packages.

00:40:08.630 --> 00:40:12.380 align:middle line:84%
But underneath, we
are all the same.

00:40:12.380 --> 00:40:16.003 align:middle line:84%
And we use our story
and our experiences

00:40:16.003 --> 00:40:17.420 align:middle line:84%
throughout the
course of our lives

00:40:17.420 --> 00:40:20.510 align:middle line:84%
as a vehicle to
have us become less.

00:40:20.510 --> 00:40:24.470 align:middle line:84%
We apply so much meaning to
what's occurred in our lives.

00:40:24.470 --> 00:40:26.390 align:middle line:90%
Somebody's unfaithful.

00:40:26.390 --> 00:40:27.380 align:middle line:90%
I'm not deserving.

00:40:27.380 --> 00:40:29.030 align:middle line:90%
I shouldn't trust men.

00:40:29.030 --> 00:40:31.250 align:middle line:84%
Or somebody goes
through a bankruptcy.

00:40:31.250 --> 00:40:32.630 align:middle line:90%
I'm bad with money.

00:40:32.630 --> 00:40:34.598 align:middle line:90%
I'll never be any good.

00:40:34.598 --> 00:40:36.890 align:middle line:84%
You know, like you hear
something when you're a child--

00:40:36.890 --> 00:40:39.380 align:middle line:90%
you never win competitions.

00:40:39.380 --> 00:40:40.640 align:middle line:90%
I'm a failure.

00:40:40.640 --> 00:40:42.830 align:middle line:84%
We attach all this
meaning to all

00:40:42.830 --> 00:40:47.690 align:middle line:84%
these insignificant occurrences
that are simply experiences.

00:40:47.690 --> 00:40:49.940 align:middle line:84%
Yes, some of them come with
challenge and some of them

00:40:49.940 --> 00:40:51.302 align:middle line:90%
come with contrast.

00:40:51.302 --> 00:40:52.760 align:middle line:84%
But there's a real
point that we're

00:40:52.760 --> 00:40:54.740 align:middle line:84%
missing is that the
contrast and the challenge

00:40:54.740 --> 00:40:56.960 align:middle line:84%
is designed to have
us become more.

00:40:56.960 --> 00:40:58.700 align:middle line:84%
It's not designed to
have us become less.

00:40:58.700 --> 00:41:01.040 align:middle line:84%
We live in an
expanding universe.

00:41:01.040 --> 00:41:05.660 align:middle line:84%
We are constantly evolving
and changing physiologically,

00:41:05.660 --> 00:41:07.170 align:middle line:90%
biologically.

00:41:07.170 --> 00:41:13.130 align:middle line:84%
So why would our conscious
experience and awareness

00:41:13.130 --> 00:41:15.260 align:middle line:84%
through our experiences
have us become less

00:41:15.260 --> 00:41:17.990 align:middle line:84%
when the whole aim of
life is to become more?

00:41:17.990 --> 00:41:20.060 align:middle line:84%
Either way, we're
landing up in a box.

00:41:20.060 --> 00:41:21.200 align:middle line:90%
That's the way I see it.

00:41:21.200 --> 00:41:22.490 align:middle line:84%
Either way, we're
landing up in a box.

00:41:22.490 --> 00:41:24.230 align:middle line:84%
We're either going to get
there with this belief that

00:41:24.230 --> 00:41:25.340 align:middle line:90%
were useless and hopeless.

00:41:25.340 --> 00:41:26.690 align:middle line:84%
Or we're going to get
there with this belief

00:41:26.690 --> 00:41:28.220 align:middle line:90%
that everything is possible.

00:41:28.220 --> 00:41:30.200 align:middle line:90%
Let me give it a go.

00:41:30.200 --> 00:41:32.840 align:middle line:84%
And through my
experiences, it had

00:41:32.840 --> 00:41:36.590 align:middle line:84%
